        }
        
        return (null != lookupList ? lookupList : Collections.EMPTY_LIST);
    }

With `Java 9`, you can now use the static factory method [List::of](https://docs.oracle.com/javase/9/docs/api/java/util/List.html#of--) to create an immutable empty list:

